                <span>News</span>
            </div>
            <div class="link_cont">
                <i class="bi bi-mortarboard"></i>
                <span>Tutorials</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="tutorials">
        <div class="featured">
            <div class="swiper-cont">
                <div class="fswipe-prev">
                    <i class="bi bi-caret-left-fill"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="fswipe-next">
                    <i class="bi bi-caret-right-fill"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="fswipe-pagination">
                    <span data-fswipe_tabIndex="1" class="active"></span>
                    <span data-fswipe_tabIndex="2"></span>
                    <span data-fswipe_tabIndex="3"></span>
                    <span data-fswipe_tabIndex="4"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-images">
                    <a href="/images/misc/tutorial1.webp" data-fswipe_tabIndex="1" class="active">
                        <img src="/images/misc/tutorial1.webp">
                    </a>
                    <a href="/images/misc/tutorial2.webp" data-fswipe_tabIndex="2">
                        <img src="/images/misc/tutorial2.webp">
                    </a>
                    <a href="/images/misc/tutorial3.jpg" data-fswipe_tabIndex="3">
                        <img src="/images/misc/tutorial3.jpg">
                    </a>
                    <a href="/images/misc/tutorial4.jpg" data-fswipe_tabIndex="4">
                        <img src="/images/misc/tutorial4.jpg">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="featured_description">
                <div class="fdesc active" data-fswipe_tabIndex="1">
                    <h4>Writing about animals</h4>
                    <span>In this tutorial, we will examine how we can give life to animals. Writing an animal is not as
                        simple as you might think!</span>
                </div>
                <div class="fdesc" data-fswipe_tabIndex="2">
                    <h4>Educated writing</h4>
                    <span>We will write super duper fancy stuff by using advanced language. You will never want to write
                        plain and simple narration ever again.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="fdesc" data-fswipe_tabIndex="3">
                    <h4>Be sophisticated</h4>
                    <span>You must sometimes refer to different cultures to show your difference from
                        peasant writers. Ever heard of the Red Ogre who cried?</span>
                </div>
                <div class="fdesc" data-fswipe_tabIndex="4">
                    <h4>Punctuation</h4>
                    <span>Yes, for the first time you will use ; : ~ - correctly.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="tcates-title">Tutorials</h3>
        <div class="tutorial-categories">
            <a href="#" class="tcate">
                <div class="tcate-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-mortarboard"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="tcate-body">
